Comment.Text: This Scenario is set for a g.tec cap with 2 amplifier g.USBamp

OVERVIEW Change Settings on Scenario Configuration tab : Scripts path = folder to the scripts and config files (normally don't need to change that if you keep the hierarchy) EMG Low/High Cut Frequency = Frequency for the temporal filter on EMG Monitoring Alpha Low/High Cut Frequency = Frequency for the temporal filter on Alpha Monitoring Low/High Cut Frequency = Frequency for the temporal filter on classical Monitoring You can enable/disable displays (last line) with right click on it and select enable/disable option.

PRESENTATION Les options sont modifiables dans l'onglet Scenario Configuration : Scripts path = dossier des scripts et des fichiers de configuration (normalement, il n'est pas ncessaire de changer cela si vous conservez la hirarchie) EMG Low/High Cut Frequency =Frquence du filtre temporel pour le monitoring EMG Alpha Low/High Cut Frequency = Frquence du filtre temporel pour le monitoring Alpha Low/High Cut Frequency = Frquence du filtre temporel pour le monitoring classique Vous pouvez activer/dsactiver les displays (dernire ligne) en faisant un clic droit dessus et en slectionnant l'option enable/disable.
